that’d be dishonest. If we’re being real, the magic in this dish is the stunning sumac roasted potatoes delicately topped with a
smattering of crumbly cheese. It's crispy, filling, earthy and indulgent. We could go on and on, but we’ll let you get on with the eating.
Bon appetite!

